summary: In 2024, Hanukkah and Christmas will coincide on December 25th, a rare occurrence. This overlap has been dubbed "Chrismukkah" by some families who celebrate both holidays. The last night of Hanukkah in 2024 will be on December 31st. The first night of Hanukkah will also be observed on December 25th, and there will be a lighting ceremony for the National Menorah. The holiday's significance and meaning will be celebrated throughout, including the message of hope from a hostage mother.

name: Tornado
summary: Severe weather has ravaged the southern United States, particularly Texas, where a tornado outbreak has left 1 person dead and at least 4 injured in Brazoria County. Confirmed tornadoes have also been reported in Jackson County, Mississippi, while a tornado watch is in effect for several counties in Georgia and South Carolina. The outbreak is part of a larger storm system that has produced tornadoes in other areas of Texas, including the Big Bend region. Video footage has captured the devastation caused by a long-track tornado that touched down in the South. The severe storms have prompted tornado warnings and watches across the region, as meteorologists monitor the situation closely.

summary: The Denver Broncos faced off against the Cincinnati Bengals in a high-stakes AFC battle with playoff implications. The game was a back-and-forth affair, with the Broncos facing a must-win situation to keep their playoff hopes alive. The Bengals played valiantly, with "Warrior" Tee Higgins and Joe Burrow leading the charge. Despite a late Broncos touchdown, the Bengals were able to secure a 30-24 overtime victory, keeping their playoff hopes alive. The game was a hard-fought battle, with the Broncos demonstrating impressive determination and a "will to compete." However, the Bengals ultimately prevailed, leaving the last AFC playoff spot still up for grabs.

name: Dayle Haddon
summary: Canadian model and actress Dayle Haddon was found dead at the age of 76 in Solebury Township, Bucks County. The suspected cause of death is carbon monoxide poisoning, as authorities believe there was a carbon monoxide leak in the home where she was staying. Haddon was a trailblazing model and actress, and her death has been met with sadness and condolences from her friends, family, and fans.
